      "title": "Diffusion -Mass transfer in fluid systems",
      "abstract": "Preface 1. Models for diffusion Part I. Fundamentals of Diffusion: 2. Diffusion in dilute solutions 3. Diffusion in concentrated solutions 4. Dispersion Part II. Diffusion Coefficients: 5. Values of diffusion coefficients 6. Diffusion of interacting species 7. Multicomponent diffusion Part III. Mass Transfer: 8. Fundamentals of mass transfer 9. Theories of mass transfer 10. Absorption 11. Absorption in biology and medicine 12. Differential distillation 13. Staged distillation 14. Extraction 15. Absorption Part IV. Diffusion Coupled with other Processes: 16. General questions and heterogeneous chemical reactions 17. Homogeneous chemical reactions 18. Membranes 19. Controlled release and related phenomena 20. Heat transfer 21. Simultaneous heat and mass transfer Problems Subject index Materials index."
